name: Maze66
description:
Maze 66 is a Horror Game where you have to escape  a crazy maze made by a psychopath to claim 6 million dollors , will you risk your life doing this??? 

Game Has 2 Endings

Story: You've been selected for a tryout in Maze 66 made by a psychopath for 6 million  dollars .will you escape or alt +f4 the game?

Avg playtime:15 minutes.

Controls: WASD to move , SHIFT to Sprint, F to interact

Install Instructions : Extract .zip  or rar  choice and play

This game will serve as A future game Concept!
